{"tid":2197544,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"689係天水圍落區個日,係唔係引入流氓對付社運人士先例?","createTime":"2020-09-10T16:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T04:51:15.000Z","uid":282637,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6982d69f1c25d9570261cd1d5409214849b5ee7f","tid":2197544,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T16:28:19.000Z","msg":"2013.08.11 - 梁振英到天水圍落區 場外起衝突 - 1<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kh2aD7IlX4M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dkh2aD7IlX4M&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=84f12063\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kh2aD7IlX4M</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2015-12-30/%E6%9B%BE%E6%85%B6%E7%B4%85%E5%9F%B9%E6%A4%8D%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1%E9%BB%91%E5%B9%AB%E4%BA%82%E6%B8%AF-33441461\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2015-12-30%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%2585%25B6%25E7%25B4%2585%25E5%259F%25B9%25E6%25A4%258D%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25B9%25AB%25E4%25BA%2582%25E6%25B8%25AF-33441461&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=550c40ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2015-12-30/%E6%9B%BE%E6%85%B6%E7%B4%85%E5%9F%B9%E6%A4%8D%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1%E9%BB%91%E5%B9%AB%E4%BA%82%E6%B8%AF-33441461</a><br />\n曾慶紅培植梁振英黑幫亂港<br />\n<img src=\"https://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/759/a1-3@1200x1200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2F759%2Fa1-3%401200x1200.jpg&h=6bccd58e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁振英上任後被指「黑幫亂港」。2013年8月11日，他到天水圍出席地區論壇，場內場外都有黑幫成員護駕。有份出席「江湖飯局」的屏山鄉鄉委會主席曾樹和（草帽者），被發現在現場指揮黑道人士圍毆示威者。（大紀元資料圖片）<br />\n梁振英上任後被指「黑幫亂港」。2013年8月11日，他到天水圍出席地區論壇，場內場外都有黑幫成員護駕。有份出席「江湖飯局」的屏山鄉鄉委會主席曾樹和（草帽者），被發現在現場指揮黑道人士圍毆示威者。（大紀元資料圖片）<br />\n林怡、何佳慧報道<br />\n2015年12月30日<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20131008/VW5IVM7SFWRGVGQITNQY3BNINA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20131008%2FVW5IVM7SFWRGVGQITNQY3BNINA%2F&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=f0421792\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20131008%2FVW5IVM7SFWRGVGQITNQY3BNINA%2F&h=2c7df519\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20131008/VW5IVM7SFWRGVGQITNQY3BNINA/</a><br />\n<br />\n挺梁振英新勢力 <br />\n與黑幫千絲萬縷<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6UBVlZY3wyfzLwiKOMS1I9S9yM4=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WEERHUFXHROVM6G7L7SM3GESKY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6UBVlZY3wyfzLwiKOMS1I9S9yM4%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWEERHUFXHROVM6G7L7SM3GESKY.jpg&h=ed725690&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾樹和當日號召大批口罩青年到天水圍特首論壇挺梁。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特首梁振英8月「頭炮」天水圍「維穩騷」，彈出一批挺梁新勢力「黑色梁粉」，包括當日號召天水圍北五條屋邨人馬到場的曾樹和、低調幕後指揮的「四眼民」、帶隊指罵反梁市民的龍獅隊負責人陳嘉輝等，有指他們與黑勢力關係千絲萬縷。<br />\n有傾有講 狀甚老友<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：江湖猛人婚宴 黑色梁粉到賀 警出動反黑組操入會場全程監控<br />\n<br />\n記者發現，維穩騷當日有份站在最前線吶喊助威，以及指罵反梁人士的一班青年，前晚均隨江湖大佬元崗村原居民「元崗黑」，以及有背景人士鄧志學出席飲宴，出出入入均在旁簇擁着。曾表示與維穩騷的「金髮梁粉」不熟識的陳嘉輝，前晚亦在婚宴門外與該名「金髮梁粉」有傾有講，不時互拍膀頭，竊竊私語，狀甚老友。<br />\n<br />\n至於去年特首選舉期間，掀起一場黑金政治風波的流浮山小桃園「江湖飯局」，座上客「囝囝」張銓漢、鄧勵東和曾樹和，前晚亦在黑色婚宴再次聚首一堂。"},{"pid":"14e382f8861db2c4ed7f979f2d358e9faeccbdd9","tid":2197544,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T16:28:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/yqlFAe6BFoHDhtcnLArdLf8I1GdhsV1oGHdED0qefKbymfcDH8m2IZ-bm3Arcczi3Wwy1NuyMWryhFrH9cv8gGVi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2FyqlFAe6BFoHDhtcnLArdLf8I1GdhsV1oGHdED0qefKbymfcDH8m2IZ-bm3Arcczi3Wwy1NuyMWryhFrH9cv8gGVi&h=731f439e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pi